1.ctrl + a goto bash commandline forward,ctrl + e goto commendline end.

2.ctrl + u delete cursor to start in commandline.ctrl + k delete cursor to end.

3.ctrl + r sreach history,run history and !(number) can run history command.

4.ctrl + l clean screen.

5.ecplise ctrl + F10 to set line number.

6.delete git file use:git rm.

7.show the file size:du -sm or du -sk.
